Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">behaviour</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> by</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> the </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">leaderships</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> of key financial institutions in both Ireland and Britain – involving high risk property lending, </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">mis</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">-selling of insurance-</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">based products and interest rate</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> manipulation – facilitated by </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">light touch regulatory regimes in each jurisdiction. In such lax regulatory environments, </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">banking leaders</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> were facilitated in </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">adopting </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">cavalier a</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">pproach</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">e</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">s – partly </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">because they believed, correc</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">tly as it turned out, that if they got into major difficulties, the Stat</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">e would assist them.</span></p><p style="marg