ight'; font-size:11pt">its</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> catastrophic mismanagement in </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">recent</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> years.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">I</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">n this context, Northern Ireland has particular concerns </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">requiring</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> special attention. We welcome </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">your</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> interest and will </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">endeavour</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> to assi</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">st </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">your </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">deliberations.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">August 2013</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div></body></html>